# 2D Idle Excavator Empire ðŸšœ

## Description
A 2D idle management game where players buy, upgrade, and manage excavators
to generate income while managing fuel resources.

## Features
- Multiple machines with upgrade levels
- Fuel consumption and refill system
- Income per second calculation
- Interactive UI panels and store system

## Tech Stack
- Unity
- C#
- Unity UI System

## What I Learned
- Game state management
- Coroutine-based systems
- Clean code architecture in Unity

